"<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<AdFitLayout>
    <data>
        <events>
            <rendered>
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/rendered1" />
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/rendered2" />
            </rendered>

            <viewable>
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/viewable1" />
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/viewable2" />
            </viewable>

            <hide>
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/hide1" />
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/hide2" />
            </hide>
        </events>
        <links>
            <link
                id="default"
                url="https://m.daum.net/">
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/click1" />
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/click2" />
            </link>

            <link
                id="cta_click"
                url="https://m.daum.net/">
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/cta_click1" />
                <tracker url="https://tracker.com/cta_click2" />
            </link>
        </links>
        <styles>
            <style>
                <colors>
                    <color id="textColor" value="#101010" />
                </colors>
                <images>
                    <image id="mainImage" url="https://t1.daumcdn.net/adfit_sdk/creatives/images/nas/img_native_ad_template_image_type_main_image.jpg" />
                    <image id="profileImage" url="https://m.daum.net/profile_image_default.png" />
                </images>
            </style>
            <style name="dark">
                <colors>
                    <color id="textColor" value="0xffffff" />
                </colors>
                <images>
                    <image id="mainImage" url="https://t1.daumcdn.net/adfit_sdk/creatives/images/nas/img_native_ad_template_image_type_main_image.jpeg" />
                </images>
            </style>
        </styles>
    </data>
    <layout>
        <Box
            width="fill"
            height="wrap">

            <!-- main image -->
            <Image
                width="wrap"
                height="wrap"
                aspectRatio="1080:720"
                url="img_native_ad_template_image_type_main_image.jpg" />

            <!-- ad info icon -->
            <Image
                width="wrap"
                height="wrap"
                margin="8"
                align="topRight"
                url="markADmark.png" />

            <Row
                width="fill"
                height="46"
                paddingHorizontal="15"
                align="bottom"
                contentAlign="center"
                background="#ffffff">

                <!-- title -->
                <Text
                    width="0"
                    height="wrap"
                    weight="1"
                    marginRight="20"
                    text="New Balance with IU"
                    textColor="#101010"
                    textSize="15" />

                <!-- cta button -->
                <Button
                    width="wrap"
                    height="wrap"
                    minHeight="28"
                    paddingHorizontal="7.5"
                    background="#ffffff"
                    backgroundCornerRadius="3"
                    backgroundBorderColor="#1f0000"
                    backgroundBorderWidth="2"
                    text="바로가기"
                    textColor="#000000"
                    textSize="14" />
            </Row>
        </Box>
    </layout>
</AdFitLayout>
"
